snippet.title: Baunsudaun Reveal & Gameplay [GAME BOY]
snippet.description:
This is a game I've been working on for the past month.  It's an actual Game Boy game so it will run on a physical Game Boy or a Game Boy emulator.  If you would like to try it for free you can do so here: https://maithonis.itch.io/baunsudaun


This game is also heavily inspired by the Funorb game Bouncedown.
